    "body": "I think any heuristic would be better than nothing - number of messages/second would be fine, but I think the best would be to limit by amount of data - so sumOfMsgSizes/second\r\nWe are already counting size in both eth68 and eth66 handlers (https://github.com/NethermindEth/nethermind/blob/master/src/Nethermind/Nethermind.Network/P2P/Subprotocols/Eth/V68/Eth68ProtocolHandler.cs#L52), we can use this value",
